@startuml
title Task 7 Coverage Evaluation Flow

actor "Golden Question Set" as golden
component "scripts/evaluate_task7.py" as evaluator
file "Task7/golden_questions.json" as goldenfile
file "Task7/golden_questions.txt" as goldentxt
file "artifacts/task7/gap_manifest.json" as gapmanifest
component "RagBot" as ragbot
database "FAISS eval index" as faiss
component "Rule-based evaluator" as rules
component "Judge model\nOllama qwen2.5:7b-instruct" as judge
file "artifacts/task7/logs.jsonl" as logs
file "artifacts/task7/eval_summary.json" as summary
file "artifacts/task7/manual_review.md" as review
file "Task7/task_7_coverage.md" as coverage

golden -> evaluator : iterate questions
goldenfile --> evaluator : load golden set\n(query, expected_outcome,\nexpected_answer, keywords,\nsources, review notes)
gapmanifest --> evaluator : load removed docs metadata
evaluator -> ragbot : answer_question(query)
ragbot -> faiss : similarity search
faiss --> ragbot : retrieved chunks
ragbot --> evaluator : RagAnswer
evaluator -> rules : evaluate(question, answer)
rules --> evaluator : pass / fail / review_needed

evaluator -> judge : review_needed only
judge --> evaluator : pass / fail / review_needed / unavailable

evaluator --> logs : append raw evaluation entry
evaluator --> summary : write aggregate metrics
evaluator --> review : write unresolved review queue
evaluator --> coverage : write coverage report

note right of goldentxt
Human-readable golden-set deliverable
for submission and manual review.
Not consumed at runtime.
end note

@enduml
